Sometimes you connect with a model different then the others. Truthfully, a lot of LA models just don’t give a shit about the photographer and their time..(they just want 5000 images or act like they don’t even want one 😂)…or attempt to connect as humans. 

Tina is different..maybe because she is a creative herself ..she has that inclusive, knowing soul of the effort it takes to create. This junkyard shoot was her vision and we all gladly took the assignment and had a blast together ❤️❤️

Thank you for trusting me (us) Tina..thank you for “getting” the whole process ..thank you for sharing the images like you’re proud of our creative day together! You are a GD Unicorn of a person 🌈💖🫶⭐️
